ays in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virginia" title=3D"Virginia=
">Virginia</a>. <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Highway_engineer" =
class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Highway engineer">Highway engineers</a> firs=
t used it to determine the optimum scope of the <a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
edia.org/wiki/Project" title=3D"Project">project</a>, and then to justify i=
