</a> to <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lawmaker" class=3D"mw-redi=
rect" title=3D"Lawmaker">lawmakers</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-15" class=3D"ref=
erence"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Analytic_hierarchy_process=
#cite_note-15"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>15<span class=3D"cite-b=
racket">]</span></a></sup>
</p><p>The weights of the AHP judgement matrix may be corrected with the on=
es calculated through the Entropy Method. This variant of the AHP method is=
 called AHP-EM.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-MDPI_2017_12-1" class=3D"reference"><a h=
ref=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Analytic_hierarchy_process#cite_note-M=
DPI_2017-12"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>12<span class=3D"cite-bra=
cket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-16" class=3D"reference"><a href=
